Performance measurement duration of a device is determined by the device management coefficient which is termed as clinical equipment management coefficient in the standard of technology & safety management series proposed by Fennigkoh et al. [25] and it was also supported by Sezdi in [19]. The equation of the clinical equipment management coefficient, ECEMC can be given [15] by Eq. (3).3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
